                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>@Template[type:emanation|distance:30] @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.bestiary-ability-glossary-srd.Aura]{Aura}</p>\n<p>The shadowforged guardian's presence dims light and brightens shadows to a strange, twilit half-light. Light can't emanate brighter than dim light in this area while darkness is simultaneously illuminated to dim light. The shadowy aura automatically attempts to counteract any 5th-level or lower magical light or darkness effect brought into this aura or created in this area (counteract check [[/r 1d20+21 #Counteract]]{+21}, 5th level). As long as the guardian is in dim light, it gains a fly Speed of 30 feet.</p>"
