                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The shadowforged guardian expels a @Template[type:cone|distance:30] of twisting shadows from its mouth. All creatures in the area must attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:29] save. The guardian can't use Shadow Breath for [[/br 1d4 #Shadow Breath Recharge]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 1} until the end of its next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is enfeebled 1 for 1 hour and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed 1} for 1 minute.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 2} for 24 hours and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed 2} for 1 minute.</p>"
